          "display": "Avalanche Summary"
        },
        "content": " <p>No avalanche activity was observed or reported.</p><p>If you head into the backcountry, thanks for sharing your observations on the<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://avalanche.ca/fr/mountain-information-network/submit\">&nbsp;</a><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://avalanche.ca/mountain-information-network/submit\">Mountain Information Network</a>&nbsp;(MIN).</p>"
